Skandia interest rates for home loan over time. Average rate per month is shown. Different lines (colours) denotes different periods of fixed rates (6 months, 1 year, 2 years, 3 years, 5 years).

Change (Slope) in fixed interest rates per month. Slope is computed over 0.5 - 2 years (slope_2), 0.5 - 3 years (slope_3) or 0.5 - 5 years (slope_5).
